{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ResolvedDocument","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","title":"ResolvedDocument","externalID":"s:10OpenAPIKit16ResolvedDocumentV","modules":[{"name":"OpenAPIKit"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ResolvedDocument","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct"},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/endpoints","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/paths","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routes","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/routesByPath","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/security","doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/underlyingDocument"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/subscript(dynamicMember:)"],"title":"Subscripts"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/Equatable-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["Linux"],"tokens":[{"text":"@dynamicMemberLookup","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ResolvedDocument","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OpenAPI documents have two distinct forms of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"distributing information such that not all relevant","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"bits of information are available in one structural","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"part of an OpenAPI Document.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Documents can contain references. This is great","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"because authors can make one part of an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenAPI document more concise by referencing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a component instead of writing it inline and it also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"allows shared definitions to be re-used throughout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the document.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Documents can define and override certain things at"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"different levels of their structure. For example, a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"document may define a shared set of Security"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Requirements at the root and then override those"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Security Requirements for particular Operations."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Both of these features of OpenAPI documents make it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"impossible to answer certain questions about a particular"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"route or endpoint without looking to multiple disparate parts"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the document and then applying certain rules to determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the relevant semantic definition of the route or endpoint being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"studied."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"OpenAPIKit defines canonical forms (i.e. the only true definitions)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of endpoints, routes, and the whole document. These types (named","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedEndpoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedRoute","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":")","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each allow you to get complete information about the respective components","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"without looking to other parts of the document.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You want to know what all of the parameters for a particular ","type":"text"},{"code":"PATCH","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" endpoint are.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Without the ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedEndpoint","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" type, you would need to look at the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenAPI.Operation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" representing the endpoint, the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenAPI.PathItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"representing the route containing the endpoint, and you would need to potentially","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resolve references to the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenAPI.Components","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"With ","type":"text"},{"code":"ResolvedDocument","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the same task is much simpler:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["let document: OpenAPI.Document = ...","","let resolvedDocument = try document","    .locallyDereferenced()","    .resolved()","","let endpoint = resolvedDocument","    .routesByPath[\"\/example\/path\"]!.patch!","","\/\/ This will be all parameters defined anywhere that","\/\/ apply to this endpoint:","let parameters = endpoint.parameters"],"syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/SQ"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openapikit\/resolveddocument"]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A resolved document is a fully dereferenced","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenAPI document that has been further distilled","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to canonical representations of each component. You","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ResolvedDocument"},{"text":" by calling the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"resolved()"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method on a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"DereferencedDocument"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OpenAPIKit/documentation/OpenAPIKit/ResolvedDocument/underlyingDocument":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenAPIKit\/documentation\/OpenAPIKit\/ResolvedDocument\/underlyingDocument","title":"underlyingDocument","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"underlyingDocument","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10OpenAPIKit20DereferencedDocumentV","text":"DereferencedDocument"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Access the underlying dereferenced document.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/openapikit\/resolveddocument\/underlyingdocument"},"doc://OpenAPIKit/documentation/OpenAPIKit/ResolvedDocument/routesByPath":{"title":"routesByPath","kind":"symbol","abstract"